2015-05-07 - 0.2

* Added SHA256 as optional hash.
* Added the max file size control.
* Added the Makefile.
* Added a manpage.
* Dropped the hardlink idea. The main goal is symbolic relative links.
  There are several options for hardlinks, as rdfind.
* Written the README.md.

